Description: Terminal UI for browsing Spark Store and APM Store
 Spark Store TUI is a Bash and fzf based terminal interface for browsing
 Spark Store and APM Store metadata, previewing application information,
 and downloading packages through Metalink and aria2c.
 .
 Debian-like systems default to Spark Store, while non-Debian systems
 default to APM Store to avoid showing incompatible Spark package content.
 .
 Downloads are stored in a temporary directory by default and cleaned up
 automatically unless KEEP_DOWNLOADS=1 is set.
